job_history.work_description: Clients have access to a broad range of services from online to in-person personal training, nutrition programming, weight loss consultations and exercise analysis. Solution focused health coaching based on readiness for change assessment, establishing trust and rapport with clients through collaborative coaching, proactive communication, use of empathy and consistency of follow-through.

Designed online personalized fitness programs to help members achieve their weight loss and physical transformation goals, achieving outstanding results by coaching 95% of testimonials used in National TV commercial campaigns, including multiple 100-pound weight loss testimonials.

Extensive one-to-one personal training experience in gyms, personal training studios and homes, providing nutritional guidance and support, guiding clients in safe exercise, taking into account individualized physical limitations.
